{"tid":398184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我同男友一齊左十年就結婚 點知發現佢有搵ex....","createTime":"2017-09-13T03:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T04:15:33.000Z","uid":53553,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a124763ad47f66519983c4d4385e95de8c45055","tid":398184,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"明明已經準備好哂年尾結婚，點解而家俾我發現佢同EX有聯絡，我知佢以前係澳洲讀書時識左個EX，拍左五年拖，係佢成世仔拍得最耐既一次，所以感情好深厚，回憶好多&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n我同佢一齊後，都覺得唔開心，因為佢會保留EX既相，佢話而家雖然對佢冇感覺，但會覺得同佢係一個好特殊既關係，呢段關係佢唔想咁易就切斷，佢都希望我接受，我無奈接受，佢亦都應承我唔會再同EX聯絡&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n後來我地拍左三年拖，感情穩定到可以發展到結婚，我真係好天真以為男朋友已經忘記左佢，以後都會屬於我，但琴日我就發現佢同EX聯絡，佢仲話好掛住個EX煮既野食，好想佢返香港煮俾佢食(我唔知係咪咩暗號..)&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n點解唔遲唔早，係要我擺哂希望落去，係要我不斷想像同佢結婚之後既生活有幾幸福，先俾我發現佢地仲藕斷絲連，感覺真係好難受..."},{"pid":"b2cbfcaa4e2407059718101b5c42b325c5bce501","tid":398184,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bf79a623959f565e183cc210a20a27a34b0fb5","tid":398184,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"朋友姐"},{"pid":"b6d17f89859ac70a311560b89f9c28c40ca5a464","tid":398184,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:00:46.000Z","msg":"打錯十年先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76e1b1f8973eddb74cf8abfb92f759069e90883","tid":398184,"uid":5278,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能"},{"pid":"650e0ba1a460003c870299265239ee0a2dfa525d","tid":398184,"uid":90609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得冇咩野<br />\n係你諗多左"},{"pid":"08e223e4fcbbdc182b74988a63f813d65eb7cfd5","tid":398184,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得冇咩野<br />\n係你諗多左</blockquote><br />\n你試過?"},{"pid":"5c4a2b4311a88cb3536313abb2f69636d398285b","tid":398184,"uid":63294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"拍左五年 成世仔最長 <br />\n<br />\n但係你又十年 <br />\n<br />\n點為之最長？"},{"pid":"255551188e1e017661f4ce53d24e7ae2631dc2cc","tid":398184,"uid":117696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍左五年 成世仔最長 <br />\n<br />\n但係你又十年 <br />\n<br />\n點為之最長？</blockquote><br />\n驗眼"},{"pid":"ff7835ae3dae003f456aca679757ac63deabe594","tid":398184,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"你地一齊左十年<br />\n佢同ex 一齊左五年 但又係最耐<br />\n但又拍拖三年就結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n五加三都冇十年啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作故前睇下自己打左咩先作ok?"},{"pid":"4d8465b0bc69a0476c6fd12fa368aac3b91daf0b","tid":398184,"uid":107417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:13:45.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能"},{"pid":"471a2277da6a24aa5f922a25bd89dfad259c6e69","tid":398184,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"你永遠唔會係佢最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}